                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430821-name-1009" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1009" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1009" type="surname" value="MALONY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1009" type="given" value="ANDREW"></interp>ANDREW MALONY</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Bennet's-place, Gracechurch-street. On the 2nd of August I was down the Commercial-road, at a meeting of Father Mathew's—the officer told me something—I felt, and missed my hand<lb></lb>kerchief—I believe this to be mine—I cannot positively swear to it—it was safe a few minutes before.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430821-name-1010" type="witnessName">
