                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1010" type="surname" value="KEMP"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-1010" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE KEMP</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable N</hi> 82.) I was on duty in plain clothes—I saw the prisoner try several pockets, and then go to the prosecutor, put his hand into his pocket, and take out this handkerchief—he put it up his jacket—I took him, and took it from him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I was in the crowd; a lad <hi rend="italic">chucked</hi> the handkerchief down at my feet; I asked the gentleman next to me if it was his; he said no, and I took it up.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
